    "an7.645-1124:1.24": "cāgāya … ",
    "an7.645-1124:1.25": "paṭinissaggāya …pe… ",
    "an7.645-1124:1.26": "ime satta dhammā bhāvetabbā”ti. ",
    "an7.645-1124:2.1": "Idamavoca bhagavā. ",
    "an7.645-1124:2.2": "Attamanā te bhikkhū bhagavato bhāsitaṁ abhinandunti. ",
    "an7.645-1124:2.3": "Rāgapeyyālaṁ niṭṭhitaṁ. ",
    "an7.645-1124:2.4": "Sattakanipātapāḷi niṭṭhitā. "
