    "an7.645-1124:1.24": "giving away … ",
    "an7.645-1124:1.25": "letting go of negligence ",
    "an7.645-1124:1.26": "these seven things should be developed.” ",
    "an7.645-1124:2.1": "That is what the Buddha said. ",
    "an7.645-1124:2.2": "Satisfied, the mendicants approved what the Buddha said. ",
    "an7.645-1124:2.3": "",
    "an7.645-1124:2.4": "The Book of the Sevens is finished. "
